<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>주문내역 - AXIO Mall</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/nav-shop') %>
<div class="container">
  <div class="page-title">주문 내역 <span class="vuln-tag">A01 - IDOR</span></div>
  <div class="alert alert-error" style="font-size:12px">
    ⚠️ 주문 상세 URL의 ID를 변경하면 타인의 주문 내역을 조회할 수 있습니다. (IDOR)
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <% if (orders.length === 0) { %>
    <p style="text-align:center;padding:32px;color:var(--text2)">주문 내역이 없습니다.</p>
    <% } else { %>
    <table>
      <tr><th>주문번호</th><th>일시</th><th>금액</th><th>상태</th><th></th></tr>
      <% orders.forEach(o => { %>
      <tr>
        <td><code>#<%= o.id %></code></td>
        <td style="color:var(--text2);font-size:12px"><%= o.created_at.slice(0,16) %></td>
        <td style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">₩<%= o.total.toLocaleString() %></td>
        <td>
          <span class="badge" style="background:<%= o.status==='pending'?'var(--accent2)':o.status==='cancelled'?'var(--red)':'var(--accent)' %>">
            <%= o.status === 'pending' ? '처리중' : o.status === 'cancelled' ? '취소됨' : o.status %>
          </span>
        </td>
        <td><a href="/shop/orders/<%= o.id %>" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">상세</a></td>
      </tr>
      <% }) %>
    </table>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
